{"type":"assistant.message","data":{"messageId":"6a4a715b-e0b2-411a-94fe-78981c46436a","content":"You're on **MSTest 3.8.2**, which supports the modern approach. Here's the recommended pattern:\n\n```csharp\n[TestClass]\npublic class MyTests : IAsyncDisposable, IDisposable\n{\n    // TestContext is injected automatically via constructor in MSTest 3.x\n    public TestContext TestContext { get; }\n\n    private HttpClient _client;\n\n    // Constructor handles synchronous init + TestContext injection\n    public MyTests(TestContext testContext)\n    {\n        TestContext = testContext;\n        _client = new HttpClient();\n    }\n\n    // Async init via IAsyncInit (or use [TestInitialize])\n    [TestInitialize]\n    public async Task SetupAsync()\n    {\n        // async per-test setup\n        await _client.GetAsync(\"https://example.com/health\");\n    }\n\n    [TestMethod]\n    public void SyncTest()\n    {\n        TestContext.WriteLine(\"Running sync test\");\n        Assert.IsNotNull(_client);\n    }\n\n    [TestMethod]\n    public async Task AsyncTest()\n    {\n        var response = await _client.GetAsync(\"https://example.com\");\n        Assert.IsTrue(response.IsSuccessStatusCode);\n    }\n\n    // Async cleanup\n    public async ValueTask DisposeAsync()\n    {\n        if (_client != null)\n            await Task.Run(() => _client.Dispose());\n    }\n\n    // Sync cleanup fallback\n    public void Dispose() => _client?.Dispose();\n}\n```\n\n**Key points for MSTest 3.x:**\n\n- **`TestContext` injection** — pass it via the constructor (no more `[TestContext]` property setter).\n- **Sync init** — use the constructor.\n- **Async init** — use `[TestInitialize] async Task` (runs before each test).\n- **Class-level async init** — use `[ClassInitialize]` on a `static async Task` method.\n- **Cleanup** — implement `IDisposable` / `IAsyncDisposable`; MSTest calls them automatically.","toolRequests":[],"interactionId":"c2a223bb-0401-4bdf-9b15-59cd8c876758","outputTokens":503,"requestId":"4C53:121281:C0B40B:EED040:6A0131A1"},"id":"5ef0c981-50b7-46d8-81dc-9eacdd727377","timestamp":"2026-05-11T01:32:27.611Z","parentId":"d517666d-da3a-4aeb-948c-182076e2a228"}
